   "source": [
    "# 🏥 Clinical Trial Matching Agent\n",
    "\n",
    "An interactive notebook that demonstrates agentic AI matching **synthetic** patient profiles to real, currently-recruiting clinical trials from [ClinicalTrials.gov](https://clinicaltrials.gov/).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Dependencies:**\n",
    "- **Amazon Bedrock** — Claude Sonnet 4 model access (for the agent and eligibility evaluation)\n",
    "- **Internet access** — to query the ClinicalTrials.gov API\n",
    "- **(Optional) Knowledge Base** — Run `setup_knowledge_base.ipynb` first if you want KB-enriched results. Without it, the agent still works using live search data.\n",
    "\n",
    "Patient profiles are embedded in-memory — no DynamoDB required.\n",
    "\n",
    "> ⚠️ **Disclaimer:** This is for **illustrative and educational purposes only**. It uses entirely synthetic patient data and is **not intended for real clinical decision-making**. A qualified physician must verify eligibility before any clinical trial enrollment decisions."
   ]
  },
  {
